{"tid":2313794,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"競馬Fact Check 直播十場沙田日馬  Paris 陳華棟 子健 富仔提供貼士","createTime":"2020-12-06T05:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T09:56:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"182619c7548e84bc65aa5c042f6d6d9e2eff970b","tid":2313794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"#Appledaily #賽馬 #競馬Fact<br />\n<br />\n競馬Fact Check<br />\n直播十場沙田日馬 <br />\nParis 陳華棟 子健 富仔提供貼士<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O4mTs79p-2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO4mTs79p-2s&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=84988115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O4mTs79p-2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.75M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n今晚（2日）快活谷馬場上演八場賽事，頭場定於晚上7時15分開跑。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果《競馬Fact Check》屆時直播各場賽事，讓馬迷恍如置身場內睇跑馬。<br />\n<br />\n《競馬Fact Check》今季新增AI模擬賽果，集各項data進行運算，識別出哪些是機會馬，以得分高低排序，一目了然。<br />\n<br />\n主持亦會即場解答網民留言，與馬迷互動交流；另外會加插騎練賽前訪問，大家或者從中可以搵到方向。<br />\n<br />\n此外，仲會新增出閘預測走位圖，等觀眾了解今場賽事形勢，邊啲馬可以賺步速；邊啲馬相對蝕底，務求幫大家捉更多冷馬！<br />\n<br />\n富仔陳志富、子健及陳華棟，與靚女評馬人Cloudy將與大家一齊直擊賽馬。<br />\n<br />\n著名評馬人廖浩賢於頭場開跑前，將作賽日大勢分析，以專業角度剖析全日重心場次及馬匹，並提供心水貼士。<br />\n<br />\n陳華棟、子健即場講沙圈、逐隻馬分析，務求幫到大家贏錢，而Cloudy亦深得馬迷喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n總之幾位主持到時都會畀貼士大家，跟住照買都無妨！<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=db2dede2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=90237a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=43be7d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=bdcd74e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android</a><br />\n=======<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8248Bk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8248Bk.jpg&h=1c44a6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2ooEH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2ooEH8.jpg&h=6aa2fa79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890f6552b8456b51f795b2e84b02e05d08e35aaf","tid":2313794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"陳嘉熙贏咗田泰安"},{"pid":"1ecf550d647875776cbfb22d880c34a6b7b0f7c0","tid":2313794,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"火天大有  $208 place"},{"pid":"c987d08cac4aa762f62861ca25253ee129980329","tid":2313794,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7b3e897ea29449d3ec7a0c1f33a584712b4db9e","tid":2313794,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三大熱"},{"pid":"5a7009df49f8533b0e12a028c5e1b9db48302c32","tid":2313794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm